///////////////////////////// WELCOME TO THE CSS | HACKTOBERFEST 2020 /////////////////////////////

CSS is a scripting Language,CSS stands for Cascading Style Sheets. It is used to describe the formatting and exterior design of a document which written in markup language (ex :HTML,XML). tTo change the style of web pages and user interfaces THIS css IS USED.
Mainly CSS is used along with HTML and JavaScript for web applications and user interfaces.


///////////////////////////// HOW WE USE CSS /////////////////////////////

There are three ways to insert CSS in HTML documents.

1.Inline CSS
2.Internal CSS
3.External CSS

/////////// 1.Inline CSS

This is used to apply CSS on a single line or element.

<h1 style="color:pink">Hacktoberfest 2020</h1>

/////////// 2.Internal CSS

This is used to apply CSS on a single document or page. It is written inside the style tag within head section of html.

<style>  
h1{color:pink}  
</style>  

/////////// 3.External CSSS

This is used to apply CSS on multiple pages or all pages. We arrange all the CSS code in a css file. It named with the extension .css .(ex:style.css) 

h1{color:pink}

Then we have to link style.css file to our html pages as follows,

<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="style.css">  